title: 'Size and colour inaccuracy but nice design'
body: Actual colour is darker than in the images (bought the greenish blue printed letter design). Okish stitching and finishing quality for the price; do not compare it with branded products. Synthetic (soft, silk-like and lightweight) material, printed design, colour doesn't fade in washing. Fitting was a problem for me and I couldn't alter it as it was too tight at a few points under arms and torso area. I really like the urban design which I actually bought the shirt for.
